	* tramp.texi: From Michael Albinus <Michael.Albinus@alcatel.de>:
	(Inline methods): Add methods `remsh' and `plink1'.
	(External transfer methods): Add method `remcp'.
	(Multi-hop Methods): Add method `remsh'.
